data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value: DupTerminator - a program to search, delete, move, and rename duplicate file by comparing MD5 hash. The program is free and open source software. Supported features: - Sort groups by column. - Select files in a specific folder, in a folder in the groups that have all folders from the selected group, by date, by name length, by specified name. - Rename files, moving files. - Delte to recycle bin. - Load / Save the list of duplicates. - Change program font, font and color of list duplicates.
